    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nCurrently, we create an output writer when we initialize the `DataWriter`: https://github.com/NVIDIA/spark-rapids/blob/7eba2eb84c84774d02ddbfe682032d67a6ae25f7/sql-plugin/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/sql/rapids/GpuFileFormatDataWriter.scala#L144\r\n\r\nWe should postpone this creation until we need an output file when writing the data. This can make our code cleaner (remove the variable `needNewWriter` and make `fileCounter` as an internal variable)\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n1. postpone the creation of new writer\r\n2. remove the variable `needNewWriter`\r\n3. make `fileCounter` as an internal variable\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nA clear and concise description of any alternative solutions or features you've considered.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nAdd any other context, code examples, or references to existing implementations about the feature request here.\r\n",
